These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different games are played: go, chess, domino, poker, scrabble, canasta, backgammon
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing poker is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 6. the american is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing chess and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
14. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
15. the person playing scrabble is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Game          | domino    | go    | chess | canasta | poker | scrabble    | backgammon |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

