.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, grapefruit, pomegranate, radish, zucchini
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, game, montecristo, siglo, dunhill, bongani, dannemann
 1. the bongani-smoker is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the person eating banana##7
 2. the dannemann-smoker is the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the game-smoker##7
 6. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the montecristo-smoker##7
 7. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating banana##7
 8. the cain-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
10. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
11. the bongani-smoker is not the person eating zucchini##6
12. the game-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | zucchini  | cabbage | radish | grapefruit | artichoke     | pomegranate | banana  |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bongani | game  | dannemann  | dunhill | siglo      | cain |

