 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person eating nectarine##7
10. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person eating papaya##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
14. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
