 4. the person eating strawberry is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in april##7
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating mango is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating raspberry and the person who's birthday is in february##2
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
13. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
15. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
